Dialogue: 0,0:00:-12.-27,0:00:-10.-26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-10.-24,0:00:-08.-36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger,\Nthe King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-08.-34,0:00:-06.-05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-06.-03,0:00:-02.-18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before\Nhis death drove people to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-02.-16,0:00:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure?\NIf you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.67,0:00:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.85,0:00:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men head for the\NGrand Line in pursuit of their dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.59,0:00:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly\Nentered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.49,0:00:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.86,0:00:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.77,0:00:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.97,0:00:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.61,0:00:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever,\NI take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it's not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.46,0:01:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.17,0:01:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard\Nsomeone else's biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.47,0:01:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn't there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.14,0:01:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.65,0:01:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.36,0:01:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand do you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.60,0:01:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.97,0:01:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.37,0:01:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Throw that gas mask away!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.71,0:01:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're no longer one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.31,0:01:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.65,0:01:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you shoot poison gas!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.89,0:02:03.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop scampering about, anchor boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.34,0:02:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.84,0:02:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ghin! You don't have to listen\Nto what that weakling says!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.68,0:02:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna kick his ass now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.85,0:02:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mock Don Krieg!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.69,0:02:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the strongest man.\NYou can't defeat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.69,0:02:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to your senses, you idiot!\NThat man is trying to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.36,0:02:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I deserve it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.20,0:02:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,since I couldn't fulfill my role,\Nshamelessly losing to emotion...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.20,0:02:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is... This is a\Nwell-deserved punishment!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.64,0:02:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ghin!\N--Why... Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.98,0:02:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha! So you showed your pride\Nat the end... But it's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.82,0:03:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die together with that cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.32,0:03:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deadly Poison Gas Bomb... M... H... 5!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.00,0:03:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I Won't Die!\NFierce Battle, Luffy vs. Krieg!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.84,0:03:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's coming!!\N--Dive into the sea!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.68,0:03:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Owner! Get inside the restaurant!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.18,0:03:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me borrow those.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.85,0:03:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji! Ghin! Use these!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.85,0:03:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Chore boy!\N--Now for mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.36,0:03:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! Everyone dived into the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.30,0:03:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh! What do I do?! What do I do?!\NWhat do I do?! What do I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.74,0:04:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.98,0:04:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is force.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.00,0:04:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I'm saved... Good thing\NI found that mask when I did...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.34,0:04:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What a crazy bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.01,0:04:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe he used\Npoison gas in battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.01,0:04:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a devil...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.02,0:04:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, no human being\Nwould do something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.63,0:04:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are Sanji and the chore boy okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.97,0:05:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not sure... Look!\NThe poison mist is clearing up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.98,0:05:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ghin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.65,0:05:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.66,0:05:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of the mask!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.66,0:05:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ghin!\N--Where's your mask?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.33,0:05:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you... give me your mask?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.34,0:05:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ghin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.34,0:05:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.01,0:05:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in pain right now\Nbecause you feel indebted
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.68,0:05:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just because someone\Ngave you some food.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.68,0:05:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess idiots\Ndon't learn until they die...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.96,0:05:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard... even after he threw\Nthe gas mask away as ordered...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.96,0:06:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that how he talks\Nto his loyal subordinate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.64,0:06:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don... Don Krieg...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.98,0:06:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ghin...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.15,0:06:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ghin... It seems...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.99,0:06:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that you picked\Nthe wrong man to follow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.50,0:06:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're actually sympathizing\Nwith that idiot scum?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.00,0:06:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Scum?!\N--That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.50,0:06:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An idiot who loses sight of our\Ngoal and can't follow my orders
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.57,0:06:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no longer holds value to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.18,0:06:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no guarantee that\Nhe won't betray me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.65,0:06:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's out of love that I put him out of\Nhis misery now. Wouldn't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.62,0:06:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I never imagined that Don would\Nactually kill the Chief Commander...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.29,0:06:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Can't be true...\NThere's no way he would!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.26,0:06:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ghin-san is his right-hand man!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.12,0:07:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. No one has been more\Nfaithful to Don than Ghin-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.63,0:07:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That time, too. When Fullbody's\NNavy ship came after us
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.10,0:07:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,right after we escaped\Nfrom the Grand Line...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.14,0:07:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... He acted as\Na decoy all by himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.24,0:07:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,pretending to be Don...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.14,0:07:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He always risked his life\Nfighting for Don Krieg...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.32,0:07:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never imagined... that Don\Nwould actually try to kill him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.16,0:07:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--How evil...\N--Patty! We have an antidote, don't we?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.66,0:07:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we do...\Nbut that's for food poisoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.00,0:07:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter what it is,\Njust bring it over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.17,0:07:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! If you wanna save him,\Nput the mask on him right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.17,0:07:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It should have some sort\Nof detoxifying effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.94,0:07:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring him to the second floor\Nand let him breathe well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.11,0:07:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's a chance to save him,\Nthat's the only way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.78,0:07:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, Patty! Carne!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.11,0:07:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right already!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.12,0:08:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.79,0:08:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha! It's no use. Even if he stays alive,\Nit'll be an hour at most...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.96,0:08:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare die, Ghin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.97,0:08:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let someone like him kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.77,0:08:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cling to life! Got that?!\NI'll kick his ass for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.81,0:08:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't. You can't... defeat him...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.31,0:08:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool down! Attacking head-on
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.75,0:08:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,would be playing right\Ninto his hands. You'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.82,0:08:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.32,0:08:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Go ahead and shoot\Nas much as you want.\N--Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.33,0:08:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a fool... The easiest enemy\Nto kill is one who's in a frenzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.60,0:08:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sea is your hell, anchor boy.\NYou're heading towards...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.44,0:08:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Here comes...\N--Bombs!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.11,0:08:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...your graveyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.77,0:09:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My graveyard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.38,0:09:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! Get out of there, chore boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.95,0:09:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He got hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.29,0:09:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.63,0:09:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chore boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.30,0:09:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You little...\N--Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.64,0:09:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hit me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.47,0:09:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Here it comes!\N--...if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.04,0:09:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dirty! That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.64,0:09:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Pistol!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.15,0:09:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.51,0:10:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don Krieg got beaten!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.18,0:10:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.48,0:10:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He hit him along with the porcupine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.69,0:10:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.69,0:10:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holy shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.36,0:10:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've never even seen\NDon brought to his knees...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.70,0:10:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He hit Don in his face! And he did it\Nthrough that Porcupine Cape!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.03,0:10:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C... Can you believe that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.38,0:10:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this... my graveyard?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.05,0:10:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or... your graveyard?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.32,0:10:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My... graveyard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.01,0:11:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think... you can send me\Nto my grave with stuff like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.02,0:11:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna die here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.04,0:11:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's crazy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.65,0:11:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see idiots like that\Nevery once in a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.99,0:12:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...ones who will fight to the death once\Nthey've set their eyes on a target...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.33,0:12:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight... to the death...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.33,0:12:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in trouble if someone\Nlike that becomes your enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.84,0:12:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know, win or lose,\NI like guys like him...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.98,0:12:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey, underling!\N--Hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.38,0:13:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, breathe!\NBreathe in a lot of good air!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.82,0:13:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right? Hey!\NDo you want to drink some water? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.66,0:13:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.00,0:13:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you wanna eat my\Nspecial pudding? It's good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.67,0:13:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! You want to feed\Npoison to a poisoned man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.34,0:13:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what do you mean by\Npoison?! You're one to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.67,0:13:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?! People say my\Nmeat dishes are the best in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.34,0:13:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're considered so delicious\Nthat people think they're in heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.15,0:13:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ahh! You can't die on us!\N--Hey! C'mon! Don't die, underling!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.12,0:13:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you dead? Are you really dead?!\NHey! Really? Are you dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.02,0:13:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Are you dead? Really?\NAre you really dead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.69,0:13:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.36,0:13:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phew, he's still alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.36,0:13:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D... Don Krieg... Is Don Krieg...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.31,0:13:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's gonna happen to this fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.31,0:13:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! That was just dumb luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:14:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way Don would be defeated\Nby a stupid brat like that! Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.98,0:14:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chore boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.32,0:14:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm not gonna die here," you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.33,0:14:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you won't die here... then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.60,0:14:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...who the hell will?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.34,0:14:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.64,0:14:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.69,0:14:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don got beaten again!\NWhat the hell is going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.96,0:14:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Enemies are supposed to die\Nwithout even touching Don Krieg...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.96,0:14:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don's supposed to be\Ninvincible... What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.47,0:15:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that brat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.99,0:15:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.66,0:15:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I'm blown away...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.16,0:15:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--He's amazing!\N--Get Krieg!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.99,0:15:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.23,0:15:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That brat is fighting Don\Nat his level, without a doubt...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.67,0:15:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a dream, right? Don getting\Nbeaten by someone like him...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.84,0:15:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don's supposed to be invincible...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.67,0:15:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As it stands, the legend of\NDon Krieg the strongest will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.67,0:15:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop talking nonsense!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.29,0:15:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.62,0:15:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,F... Finally, Don Krieg's\Nstrongest weapon...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.96,0:15:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Mighty Battle Spear!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.80,0:16:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that? It exploded.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.63,0:16:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now... I'll see how long you\Ncan keep avoiding this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.97,0:16:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a sight, anchor boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.14,0:16:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That puny spear from earlier still\Nleft you standing after a few attacks,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.64,0:16:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but this Mighty Battle Spear is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.15,0:16:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as you touch it,\Nyou'll be blown to pieces!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.99,0:16:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's with that spear?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.32,0:16:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fall, I'll fall, I'll fall...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.83,0:16:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's with that spear?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.76,0:16:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It explodes every time\Nhe strikes it down?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.00,0:16:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? My knees...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.34,0:16:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A long battle will be trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.34,0:16:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's shed too much blood...\NHe's not gonna last long...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.34,0:16:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your overdoing it has\Ntaken its toll on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.61,0:16:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be reaching your limit...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.12,0:16:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn! With the foothold\Nrocking like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.05,0:16:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't fight with full power.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.05,0:16:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm stumped.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.79,0:17:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Mighty Battle Spear\Nnever ceases to amaze me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.29,0:17:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. The stronger that\Nbig spear is struck down,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.60,0:17:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the bigger the explosion it causes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.77,0:17:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's something that no one\Nother than Don can handle!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.48,0:17:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how powerful he is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.35,0:17:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think he easily swings around\Nthat super heavy spear,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.08,0:17:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which weighs 1 ton with\Nthose two shoulder guards!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.32,0:17:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly the reason\Nwhy Don is the strongest!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Wooaahhh...\N--Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.50,0:17:45.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.94,0:17:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chore boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.61,0:17:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phew... That was close...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.95,0:17:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You... damn caterpillar!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.62,0:18:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Waaahhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.13,0:18:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chore boy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.98,0:18:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Chore boy...\N--Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.32,0:18:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha! I'm not quite done yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.32,0:18:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You made me angry.\NI won't let you die so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.60,0:18:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! That bastard Krieg brings\Nout weapons one after another...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.60,0:18:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that chore boy can...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.61,0:18:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if hundreds of\Nweapons are built in,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.14,0:19:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he can be defeated by someone\Nwith a spear of blind determination.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.96,0:19:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph! How easy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.65,0:19:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that makes you worth crushing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.99,0:19:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Life or death...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.83,0:19:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In a pirate battle, if you fear death\Nfor even a moment, you'll fall to pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.67,0:20:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.17,0:20:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.68,0:20:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.69,0:20:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that kid doesn't have any hesitation!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.37,0:20:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a survival instinct?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or does he not fear death\Nbecause he has faith in himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.45,0:20:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Faith...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.66,0:21:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y... You son of a bitch!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.84,0:21:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Alright! You're amazing!\N--Chore boy! Go for it!!\N--Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.01,0:21:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you... that this is where you die!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.02,0:21:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am the strongest man!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.37,0:21:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fleet Krieg gathered...\NHis hundreds of weapons and poison...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.07,0:21:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they're all force...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.98,0:21:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...then that kid's spear is also force...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.15,0:21:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The spear held in his heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.32,0:22:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know an idiot who's holding back\Nthat spear for a stupid reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.17,0:22:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-My Mighty Battle Spear is...\NWhat the hell did you do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.52,0:22:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gave it five punches.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.69,0:22:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's it for your spear.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.19,0:22:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.03,0:22:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was little, I had\Na vision of a treasure map
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.28,0:23:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I always searched\Nfor that miraculous place
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.22,0:23:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before someone else could\Nbeat me to it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.93,0:23:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the world is going to change
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.41,0:23:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before I can even attain my dream
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.41,0:23:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then take me to the time\Nwhen I knew nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.49,0:23:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so that my memories won't fade
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.64,0:24:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is he fighting when\Nhis body's falling apart?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.48,0:24:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he trying to get himself killed?!\NNo, he isn't even thinking about dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.15,0:24:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Risking life for an ambition and dream...\NI used to have a dream like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.49,0:24:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--This is it!!\N--Chore boy! Don't die in a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.82,0:24:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.99,0:24:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Conclusion of the Deadly Battle!\NA Spear of Blind Determination!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.83,0:24:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!
